#include<cstdio>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    long long N,A,Q,t,min,max;
    scanf("%lld %lld",&N,&Q);
    min=999999999;max=0;
    while(N--)
    {
        scanf("%lld",&A);
        if (A<min) min=A;
        if (A>max) max=A;
    }
    while (Q--)
    {
        scanf("%lld",&t);
        if (t>=min && t<=max) printf("Yes\n"); else printf("No\n");
    }
    return 0;
}
